       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=The%20WoW%20Rogue%20Reviewed&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Freviews%2Farticle_31.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
